msgctxt "268_Saki"
msgid "I'm so sorry. Won't you please forgive me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "280_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Fraudsters like you give Kamurocho's financial industry a\r\n"
"bad name. I think it's high time the police got involved."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "292_Saki"
msgid ""
"So you're in the business, too, are you? No wonder you\r\n"
"knew so much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "304_Saki"
msgid ""
"I'm begging you! I'll compensate you for your trouble. Just\r\n"
"please, please let this go－just this once!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "328_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"All right, just this once. But the next time I get wind of\r\n"
"your little scam, I might not be so generous. Got it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "340_Saki"
msgid ""
"Yes, sir! I'm so very sorry! We'll go back to making loans\r\n"
"completely legit, I swear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "364_Saki"
msgid "I'm so sorry. Won't you please forgive me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "376_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Now, this is quite the dilemma. I could always tell the\r\n"
"police you tried to bully me into a bum deal..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "388_Saki"
msgid ""
"No, please! Anything but that! Here, maybe this will help\r\n"
"smooth things over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "412_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"...Judging from this, I imagine you guys haven't been doing\r\n"
"all that well with this scam, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "424_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"I'll let it slide this time, but if you try this nonsense\r\n"
"again... I think you catch my drift."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "436_Saki"
msgid ""
"Yes, sir! I'm so very sorry! Everything will be completely\r\n"
"legit from now on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "472_Forex Company President"
msgid ""
"We appreciate your taking time out of your busy day to visit\r\n"
"with us here at Ciel Trading."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "484_Talk_Ojigi"
msgid ""
"I'm Saki, the company president, and I'll be conducting your\r\n"
"information session."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "496_Akiyama"
msgid "Wow, an audience with the president himself?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "508_Saki"
msgid ""
"Indeed! I'm very excited about the products we have to\r\n"
"offer! First, may I have your name?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "520_Akiyama"
msgid "It's Akiyama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "532_Saki"
msgid "Thank you, Akiyama-sama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "544_Akiyama"
msgid "Now, Saki-san... what exactly is this forex thing, anyway?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "556_Saki"
msgid ""
"Well, we're in the middle of a foreign exchange boom these\r\n"
"days, with all kinds of products on the market. But ours is\r\n"
"truly a cut above the rest!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "568_Saki"
msgid ""
"Are you familiar with how forex works? You make a small\r\n"
"investment and convert it into several times that amount in\r\n"
"foreign currency."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "580_Saki"
msgid ""
"You can expect high returns－ten or even one hundred times\r\n"
"your original investment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "592_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Ah, but you can just as easily lose ten or one hundred times\r\n"
"your original investment, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "604_Saki"
msgid ""
"You're absolutely right! I see you know a thing or two about\r\n"
"this after all. Those losses can be a real problem."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "616_Saki"
msgid ""
"Now, with your average forex trade, any loss becomes the\r\n"
"responsibility of the trader who put up the money."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "628_Saki"
msgid ""
"But we're different! We have absolute faith in our forex investing system, "
"so if one of our trades should fail, you can rest assured we'll cover it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "640_Akiyama"
msgid "So the investor gets nothing but profits?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "652_Saki"
msgid ""
"Exactly! Our company takes responsibility for all trades.\r\n"
"The investor doesn't have to worry about a thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "664_Saki"
msgid ""
"And at thirty to forty percent profitability on a monthly\r\n"
"basis, our results speak for themselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "676_Saki"
msgid ""
"The handling fee is just one percent of the profit, so you\r\n"
"can see how you stand to gain."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "688_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"So my money would increase by twenty-nine percent every\r\n"
"month with absolutely no losses... Neat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "700_Saki"
msgid ""
"And for a limited time, invest at least one million yen with\r\n"
"us right now, and you'll receive two hundred thousand yen\r\n"
"cash back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "712_Saki"
msgid ""
"We'll add that two hundred thousand to your investment,\r\n"
"making your profit that much greater."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "724_Akiyama"
msgid "A million yen? Right here, right now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "736_Saki"
msgid ""
"Oh, well, it's not as though we expect you to walk around\r\n"
"town with a million yen in your wallet..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "748_Saki"
msgid ""
"That's why we're offering low-interest loans, so you can get\r\n"
"your feet wet in the world of forex without dipping into\r\n"
"your savings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "760_Akiyama"
msgid "Ah, I see. Forex and loans both. Who knew?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "772_Saki"
msgid ""
"That concludes my presentation on our company's forex\r\n"
"products. Do you have any questions?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "784_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Let me see if I've got this straight. You've got a surefire\r\n"
"profit-making system, plus plenty of money available for\r\n"
"lending."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "796_Saki"
msgid ""
"You'd make a mint just investing your own money. Why solicit\r\n"
"investors and water down your profits?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "808_Saki"
msgid ""
"Er, well, uh... Our company's motto is \"Contribute to\r\n"
"society,\" so..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "820_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"And a noble motto it is. If only other financial firms would\r\n"
"follow your lead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "832_Saki"
msgid ""
"We also see value in a spirit of volunteerism going\r\n"
"forward..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "844_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"It sounds like I'd make out like a fat rat, but does your\r\n"
"company profit from this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "856_Saki"
msgid ""
"Yes, we're grateful for the many clients who've invested\r\n"
"with us. Our company is growing, and our profits are\r\n"
"constantly on the rise!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "868_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Ah, so you spread the profits thin and wide. That's one way\r\n"
"to do it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "880_Saki"
msgid "Did, uh, you have any other questions?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "892_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"If something should happen, will I get back the money I\r\n"
"originally invested?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "904_Saki"
msgid ""
"But of course! Our company compensates for any loss with its\r\n"
"own money, so your initial investment will never decrease!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "916_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Provided the company stays in business, you mean. What I\r\n"
"want to know is what if the company goes under? Can I still\r\n"
"recover that deposit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "928_Saki"
msgid ""
"Would it be a trust account? Is the investor's money kept\r\n"
"separate from the company funds, stashed away nice and safe\r\n"
"in a bank somewhere?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "940_Saki"
msgid "Yes, of course... at, uh, Touto Bank..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "952_Akiyama"
msgid "Touto Bank!? Are you sure you don't mean Touto Trust?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "964_Saki"
msgid ""
"Oh, yes－that's the one! My mistake! Your investment is\r\n"
"deposited at Touto Trust, where it's safe and sound!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "976_Akiyama"
msgid "So is profit absolutely guaranteed?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "988_Saki"
msgid ""
"I'm glad you asked! If you make a profit, it's yours. If you\r\n"
"take a hit, our company covers it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1000_Saki"
msgid ""
"In theory, as long as you have a contract with us, you'll\r\n"
"make a profit 100 percent of the time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1012_Akiyama"
msgid "100 percent, huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1024_Saki"
msgid ""
"So what do you think? Have I convinced you of our program's\r\n"
"many benefits yet?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1036_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"It's nothing but a scam. You lure people in with your\r\n"
"absurd, pie-in-the-sky BS, sign them on for a loan, and\r\n"
"send them on their way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1048_Saki"
msgid ""
"Then you pull the plug on the company, leaving the deposits\r\n"
"in limbo. Ah, but those loans－they're not going anywhere...\r\n"
"That about right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1060_Talk_No"
msgid ""
"I doubt you've ever traded forex in your life. If you're\r\n"
"going to cheat people, at least do your homework first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1072_Saki"
msgid "Huh? Hey..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1132_Saki"
msgid "Hold it right there, pal!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1180_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"I can't say I'm entirely convinced. I'm going to have to\r\n"
"pass..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1192_Saki"
msgid "Huh? Hey..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1264_Saki"
msgid "Wait just a moment, please, sir..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1360_Saki"
msgid ""
"Our entire staff will use any means necessary to convince\r\n"
"you to sign a contract... even excessive force!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1384_Akiyama"
msgid "Who knows? This might be my chance. Where do I sign?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1396_Saki"
msgid ""
"Thank you very much! Now, you're interested in the one\r\n"
"million yen loan option today, is that correct?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1408_Saki"
msgid "Allow me to prepare the necessary paperwork..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1432_Saki"
msgid "Does your company profit from this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1444_Saki"
msgid "Why should I put up any money?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1456_Saki"
msgid "Sign me up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1468_Saki"
msgid "Can I get my investment back, no matter what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1480_Saki"
msgid "Is profit absolutely guaranteed?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1492_Saki"
msgid "All right, let's do this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1504_Saki"
msgid "It's nothing but a scam."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1516_Saki"
msgid "I think I'll pass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1528_Saki"
msgid "You bet! Where do I sign?"
